column5: I have been out fishing the rec canal towards evening and on the last few trips have found some decent crappie. One even over 11".  Has anyone else gotten them in the canal or river lately?  Thinking of tight lines!
hey Ranger how goes it??? Glad to see u got into some decent fish. PM me if u need some specifics only maybe another week or 2 for the crappie there, but the bluegill are a plenty, good luck!
